                <p style="font-family: Arsenal, sans-serif;color: var(--dark);"><br><span style="text-decoration: underline;">XYL Capital </span>Pty Ltd is a 100 % truly black owned, managed and controlled company based in South Africa, it was established in 2013. XYL Capital has invested as a minority shareholder in at least 46 Johannesburg Stock Exchange (JSE) listed companies and 24 diverse portfolios, that includes Financial Sector, Banking Sector, Mining Sector, Metal Sector, ICT Sector, Printing Sector.<br></p>
